xtent of cold dust in spiral disks (which is\npoorly known). It may also represent a lower limit if galaxies expel dust over\ntime into the intergalactic medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2000 13:55:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
